devdoc.author: Chris Martin

addValue(bytes).details: adds the msg value to the value of the lockBox

params.answers: serialised lockBox answers answer serialisation form is <numberOfAnswers(1byte)><answer1(32 bytes)>...<answerN(32 bytes)>
params.hints: serialised lockBox hints hint serialisation form is <numberOfHints(1byte)><sizeOfHint1(2 bytes)><hint1>...<sizeOfHintN(2 bytes)><hintN>
params.numAnswersRequired: number of correct answers required to unlock this lockBox
params.unlockingPeriod: number of blocks before redeemer can claim unlocked value

getOwnedLockBoxId(uint256).details: returns the id of a lockBox given its index in the ownedLockBoxes mapping

getOwnedLockBoxesCount().details: returns the number of lockBoxes where the sender is the owner

redeemLockBox(bytes,uint256,address).details: given that the lockBox is redeemable by the msg sender, sends specified amount to specified address

spendFromLockBox(bytes,uint256,address).details: bypass redemption and immediately send the specified value to a chosen address

unlockLockBox(bytes,bytes).details: given the correct hash inputs for the answers, sets the sender as the redeemer of the lockBox
